      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAYFAIR SHINE (5) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Marissa Vella (30.25) in a Grade 5. Has ability and can bounce back. ANNDAR SPIRIT (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (25.92) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ROBELL SETH (4) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (25.91) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Can feature with the right run. UNRECOVERABLE (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
